quran[112]{c,v,t}:
  21,1,"Nnipa nkontabuo (berε no) abεn wͻn, nanso wͻ’de anibianaso twi fa so"
  21,2,"Afutusεm foforͻ biara a ebefri wͻn Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ aba wͻn hͻ no, gyesε wͻ’tie no agodie mu (anaasε wͻ’fa no fεwdie)"
  21,3,"Nsεm hunu na ԑwᴐ wͻn akoma mu. Abͻneεfoͻ no tu agyina kokoa mu (ka sε): “Woi nyε nipa sε moara? Mode moho bεma ntafowa anaa naadaasεm aberε a moani tua?”"
  21,4,"(Nkͻmhyεni) kaa sε: “Me Wura Nyankopͻn Nim asεm biara a εwͻ soro ne asaase so, na Ɔne Otiefoͻ no a Ɔte biribiara, na Ɔno ara ne Onimdefoͻ no a Onim biribiara no"
  21,5,"Daabi, wͻ’ka sε: (Saa Adiyisεm yi tesε) daeε so bi a adi afra. Daabi, w’abͻ netrim (na atwerε), Daabi, ͻyε dwom-toni! (Sε εnte saa a) εneε ͻnfa nsεnkyerεnee bi sεdeε yεde somaa tetefoͻ no (asomafoͻ no) bi mmrε yεn“"
  21,6,Nkuro a Ye’dii wͻn anim kan sεee wͻn no mu biara nnihͻ a wͻ’gye diiε. Enti wͻn bεgye adi anaa
  21,7,"(Wᴐn a) Y’edii w’anim kan somaa wᴐn no na wᴐ‎’yԑ nnipa na Ye’yii Adiyisεm no maa wͻn. Enti (Makafoͻ a moregye Muhammad akyinnyeε) sε monnim a, momisa wͻn a wͻ’kaekae (amanfoͻ) no"
  21,8,"Na Y’amma Asomafoͻ no honam a enni aduane, na Y’annyε wͻn (nnipa a) wͻ’bεtena (wiase) afe bͻͻ (na wͻn nwuo)"
  21,9,"Enti Yedii bͻhyε no ho nokorε maa wͻn, na Y’εgyee wͻn ne wͻn a Y’εpε no nkwa, na Y’εsεee nsεmͻnedifoͻ no"
  21,10,"(Adasamma), ampa sε Y’asiane Nwoma a moho afutusεm, moanimuonyam ne monkͻsoͻ ho asεm wͻ mu. Enti monnte (saa adom kεseε yi) ase"
  21,11,Nkuro dodoɔ sɛn na na wͻ’yε abͻneεfoͻ a Yε’sεee no? Ɛno akyiri no Yε’bͻͻ nnipa foforͻ (dehyεε wͻn anan mu)
  21,12,"Ɛberε a wͻ’hunuu Y’asotwee no, hwε! (Wͻ’bͻͻ mmͻden sε) wͻ’redwane no"
  21,13,"Monhwε na moandwane, na mmom monsan nkͻ moahodwoͻ abrabͻ a mowͻ mu no mu, ne moasetena a mowͻ mu no mu sεdeε yεbebisa mo asεm"
  21,14,"Wͻ’kaa sε: Adi ayε yεn! Nokorε sε na yε’yε abͻneεfoͻ"
  21,15,Wͻn suu no deε anyae kͻpem sε Yε’yεε wͻn sε afuo a yatwa emu nnͻbae na atεm dinn
  21,16,Ɛnyε agorͻ nti na Yεbͻͻ soro ne asaase ne deε εwͻ mfinfii no
  21,17,"Sε Yε’pε anigyesεm (sε εyerε anaa mma) a, anka Yε’bεfa no wͻ Yεn hͻ, sε Yε’pε sε yεyε (saa a)"
  21,18,"Daabi, Yε’to Nokorε no bͻ nkontompo no, na (nkontompo no) atu ayera afri hͻ korakora; na hwε na nkontompo asopa. Adi nyε mo wͻ (nkontomposεm a) mode susu (Nyankopͻn) no"
  21,19,"Nea ԑwͻ soro ne asaase soͻ (nyinaa) yε Nedea. Wͻn a wͻn wͻ Nehͻ (Soro abͻfoͻ) no nnyε Nesom ho ahomasoᴐ, na εnha wͻn anaasε wͻ’mmrε nso (wͻ Nesom ho)"
  21,20,Wͻ’bͻ (no) abodin kamfo no anadwo ne adekyeε (mu nyinaa) na wͻ’mmrε
  21,21,Anaasε wͻn anya anyame bi wͻ asaase no so a wͻ’yane awufoͻ
  21,22,"Sε anyame bi wͻ soro ne asaase so ka Nyankopͻn ho a anka (ͻsoro ne asaase) mmienu (nyinaa) asεe. Kronkron Hene ne Nyankopͻn, Animuonyam ahennie Wura no, Ɔso kyεn sεdeε wͻ’de susu no no"
  21,23,"Obiara ntumi mmisa no wͻ deε Ɔyε ho asεm, na wͻn deε yεbebisa wͻn"
  21,24,"Anaasε wͻn afri N’akyi anya anyame foforͻ bi? (Nkͻmhyεni), ka sε: “Monfa mo nyinasoͻ mmra. Woi ne afutusεm dema wͻn a wͻ’ka me ho ne wͻn a wͻ’dii m’anim kan no. Daabi, wͻn mu pii nnnim Nokorε no, enti wͻ’dane wͻn ho fri ho"
  21,25,"(Nkͻmhyεni), ͻsomafoͻ biara a Ye’dii w’anim kan somaa no no, Adiyisεm a Ye’yi maa no ara ne sε, (ͻmͻ amanfoͻ no kͻkͻ) sε: “Awurade foforͻ biara nni hͻ gyesε Me nko ara enti monsom Me “"
  21,26,"Wͻ’keka sε: “Ahummͻborͻ Hene no awo ba. Kronkron Hene ne no. Daabi, wͻn (a wͻ’ka sε wͻ’yε Nyankopͻn mma tesε soro abͻfoͻ ne Yesu no nyinaa) yε (Nyankopͻn) nkoa animuonyamfoͻ"
  21,27,"Wͻ’nni Nyankopͻn anim kan nnkasa, na mmom N’ahyεdeε so na (wͻ’gyina) yε wͻn adwuma"
  21,28,"Onim deε εda wͻn anim ne deε εda wͻn akyi na wͻ’nntumi ntwitwa nnye (obi) gye nea W’agye no ato mu, na Neho suro ma wͻn ho popo"
  21,29,Wͻn mu nea ͻbefri N’akyi aka sε; “Me yε Nyame” no saa (nipa no) Yε’de Amanehunu gya na ebetua ne so ka. Na saa na Ye’tua abͻneεfoͻ no so ka
  21,30,"Enti (Kaafirfoͻ) boniayεfoͻ no nhunuu sε na anka ͻsoro ne asaase bͻ mu (baako) εna Yε’paee mu? Ɛna adeε a εwͻ nkwa biara Yε’de nsuo na εyͻeε, enti wͻ’nnye nni anaa"
  21,31,"Ɛna Y’ayε mmepͻ de asisi asaase no so pintinn sεdeε εmma (asaase no) nnwoso wͻn, εna Y’atwitwa akwan a εterε wͻ soͻ sεdeε wͻ’bεnante kwan tenenee soͻ"
  21,32,"Ɛna Y’ayε ͻsoro sε (efie) nkurusoͻ a yεwεn, nanso wͻ’dane wͻn ho fri emu nsεnkyerεnee no ho"
  21,33,Ɔno na Ɔbͻͻ adesaeε ne adekyeε ne awia ne bosome. Emu biara wͻ kwan a εnam soͻ
  21,34,"(Nkͻmhyεni), Yε’nyεε onipa biara nnii w’anim kan sԑ ᴐbԑtena (wiase) afe bͻͻ. Enti sε wowu a wͻn deε wͻ’bεtena (wiase) afe bͻͻ anaa"
  21,35,"Ɔkra biara bεka owuo ahwε. Yε’de bͻne ne papa nso bεsͻ mo ahwε, na Yε’hͻ na mobεsan aba"
  21,36,"Sε wͻn a wͻ’po nokorε no hu wo a, deε wͻ’yε fa wo ho ara ne sε wͻ’bedi wo ho fεw (aka sε): “Woi na ͻrekasa fa mo abosom no ho no?” Ahummͻborͻ Hene abodin no deε wͻ’mpε"
  21,37,"Yε’bͻͻ onipa wͻ ntԑmpԑ suban mu. Mεkyerε mo Mensεnkyerεnee, enti εmma mommisa Me sε εmmra ntεm"
  21,38,"Deԑ wͻ’ka ne sε: “Ɛberε bεn na saa bͻhyε no besie, sε moyε nokwafoͻ ampa a?”"
  21,39,Sε wͻn a wͻ’yi boniayε no nim εberε a wͻ’ntumi nnyi egya no mfri wͻn anim anaa wͻn akyi na yεmmoa wͻn no (siteε) a
  21,40,"Daabi, εbεba wͻn so mpofirem, na wͻ’bεyε basaa, na wͻ’ntumi nnsi ano kwan, na yεmma wͻn ahomegye berε nso"
  21,41,"Ampa sε wͻ’dii asomafoͻ a wͻ’dii w’annim kan no ho fεw, na wͻn a wͻ’dii fεw no, deε wͻ’dii ho fεw no betwaa wͻn ho hyiae"
  21,42,"Kasε: “Hwan na obetumi abͻ mo ho ban afri Ahummͻborͻ Hene no nsam wͻ anadwo ne adekyeε mu? Daabi, (obiara nnihͻ), nanso wͻ’dane wͻn ho fri wͻn Wura Nyankopͻn abodin ne Nenkaekaeε ho"
  21,43,Anaasε wͻn wͻ anyame a wͻ’bεbͻ wͻn ho ban afri Yεn hͻ? Wͻ’nni tumi a wͻ’de boa wͻn ho na kampεsε wͻ’abͻ wͻn ho ban afri Yεn (asotwee) mu
  21,44,"Daabi, Yε’bͻͻ woi nom ne wͻn agyanom akͻnhoma kͻpem sε nkwa (nna no) yεε (wͻn ani so) tenten maa wͻn. Enti (boniayεfoͻ no) nhunuu sε Yε’rete nsaase (a na wͻ’di so tumi no) so nkakrankakra firi ahyeε no soͻ? Enti wͻn na wͻ’bedi nkonim"
  21,45,"(Nkͻmhyεni), kasε: “Medeε Adiyisεm no na mede bͻ mo kͻkͻ, na ͻsosifoͻ no deε, sε yεbͻ no kͻkͻ mpo a ͻnnte frε no.“"
  21,46,"Ampa sε wo Wura Nyankopͻn asotwee no ho mframa sͻ wͻn mu a wͻ’bεka sε: “Adi ayε yεn. Nokorε sε na yεyε abͻneεfoͻ”"
  21,47,"Yε’de nokorε nsania no besi hͻ ama Wusͻreε da no, na yennsisi ͻkra biara ketekete koraa. Sε (ne dwuma pa anaa bͻne) mu duro tesε wisa aba mpo a Yε’de bεba (akontabuo mu). Na Yε’sombo wͻ akontabuo ho"
  21,48,"Nokorε sε Yεde Furqaan maa Mose ne Aaron, ne nhyerεnee ne afutusεm dema Nyame surofoͻ no"
  21,49,"Wͻn a wͻ’suro wͻn Wura Nyankopͻn wͻ nsumaeε mu no, wͻn na wͻ’bͻ hu wͻ Dͻnhwere no ho"
  21,50,Saa (Qur’aan) yi yε Afutusεm a nhyira wͻ mu a Y’asiane; enti mobεpo anaa
  21,51,"Ampa sε Ye’dii kan de Abraham kwankyerε maa no, na na Ye’nim no yie (fa negyidie ho)"
  21,52,"Ɛberε a ͻka kyerεε na’gya ne nenkorͻfoͻ sε: “Ɛdeεn ne saa ahonin a mode moho ama resom wͻn yi?”"
  21,53,"Wͻ’buaa sε: “Yε’bεtoo Yε’agyanom sε wͻ’resom wͻn"
  21,54,"Ɔkaa sε: “Ampa sε mo ne moagya nom (nyinaa) wͻ ͻyera pefee mu paa“"
  21,55,"Wͻ’kaa sε: “Wode nokorε na aberε yεn anaasε woka wͻn a wͻ’di fεw no ho?”"
  21,56,"Abraham kaa sε: “Daabi, Mo Wura Nyankopͻn no, Ɔne ͻsoro ne asaase Wura a Ɔbͻͻ (soro ne asaase) no, na medeε meka wͻn a wͻ’di woi ho adanseε no ho"
  21,57,"“Medͻ Nyame sε: “Ansa na mobεkͻ adane moakyi asan aba no, na m’abͻ moabosom no ho pͻ (asεe no) “"
  21,58,"Enti obubuu (abosom no) asinasin, na mmom (ogyaa) wͻn mu kεseε no sεdeε wͻ’bεsan abεto no"
  21,59,"(Wͻ’behunuiε no) wͻ’kaa sε: “Hwan na wayε yεn anyame yi seyie? Nokorε sε (saa nipa no), ka abͻneεfoͻ no ho “"
  21,60,"Wͻ’kekaa sε: “Yε’tee sε abranteε bi rekeka wͻn ho asεm (bɔne), yεfrε no Abraham”"
  21,61,"Wͻ’kaa sε: “Monfa no mmra nnipa no anim sεdeε wͻ’bedi ho adanseε ”"
  21,62,"Wͻ’bisaa sε: “Abraham wo na woyεε yεn anyame no seyie yi?”"
  21,63,"Abraham kaa sε: “Daabi, wͻn mu (bosom) kεseε woi na ayε, enti sε (abosom no) kasa a, εneε momisa wͻn“"
  21,64,"Enti wͻ’dwenee ho wͻ wͻn ara wͻn mu, na wͻ’kekaa sε: “Nokorε sε moka abͻneεfoͻ no ho “"
  21,65,"Aniwuo maa wͻ’sisii wͻn ti ase (kaa sε): “(Abraham), wonim yie sε (abosom) woi nom nnkasa “"
  21,66,Abraham kaa sε “Enti mofri Nyankopͻn akyi som adeε a entumi mma mo mfasoͻ biara na entumi mfa ͻhaw biara nso mma mo?”
  21,67,“Moani awu wͻ deε mofri Nyankopͻn akyi som no ho. Enti monni adwen?”
  21,68,"Wͻ’kaa sε: “Monhye no na mommoa mo anyame, sε mobԑyε (no biribi) a"
  21,69,"Yε’kaa sε: ”Egya, yε nyunu ne asomdweε ma Abraham “"
  21,70,Wͻ’hwehwεε sε wͻ’bͻ (Abraham) ho pͻ bͻne enti Yε’maa wͻ’yεε berεguofoͻ
  21,71,Yε’gyee Abraham ne Lut nso nkwa de wͻn kͻͻ asaase a Y’ahyira so ama amansan no so
  21,72,"Na Yε’de Is’haaq kyεε no, εna (Yε’yεε) Ya’aquub nso ntosoͻ (maa no), na Yε’maa wͻn mu biara yεε nipa papa"
  21,73,"Yε’yεε wͻn akandifoͻ a wͻ’de Y’ahyεdeε no kyerε (amanfoͻ) kwan, na Ye’yii papayε ne Nyamefrε ne Zaka yie maa wͻn, na (Yεnko ara na na) wͻ’som Yεn"
  21,74,"Lut nso Yε’maa no nyansa ne nimdeε, na Yε’gyee no fri kuro no a na wͻ’yε akyiwadeε no mu. Nokorε sε na wͻ’yε nnipa bͻnefoͻ, ahohwifoͻ"
  21,75,Yε’de no wuraa Y’ahummͻborͻ no mu. Nokorε sε na ͻka apapafoͻ no ho
  21,76,"Noa nso, εberε a odii kan su frεε Yεn no, Yε’gyee no so, na Yε’gyee no ne n’abusuafoͻ frii mmusuo kεseε no mu"
  21,77,Yε’boaa no gyee no frii amanfoͻ no a wͻ’faa Yεn Nsεm no atorͻsεm no nsam. Nokorε sε na wͻ’yε nnipa bͻnefoͻ. Enti Yε’maa nsuo faa wͻn nyinaa
  21,78,"Dawid ne Solomon nso, εberε a wͻ’buu atεn wͻ afuo bi a nkorͻfoͻ bi nnwan kͻͻ mu adidie anadwo no ho no, na Ye’di wͻn atemmuo no ho adanseε"
  21,79,"Enti Yε’maa Solomon nyaa (asεm no) ho nteaseε. Wͻn mu biara, Yε’maa (no) nyansa ne adwen; na Yε’brεε mmepͻ ne nnomaa ase kaa Dawid ho maa wͻ’bͻͻ Yεn abodin. Yεn na Yε’yεε (woi nom nyinaa)"
  21,80,"Yε’kyerεε Dawid (sεdeε) ͻbεyε dadeε akotadeε ama mo, sεdeε εbεbͻ moho ban wͻ ͻkoo mu. Enti mobeyi (Nyankopͻn) ayε anaa"
  21,81,Solomon nso (Yε’brεε) mframa a na ԑnam n’ahyԑdeԑ so bͻ dendenden kͻ asaase a Y’ahyira so no soͻ no ase maa no. Na Yε’wͻ biribiara ho nimdeε
  21,82,"Abonsamfoͻ no mu bi wᴐ hᴐ a wͻ’dͻ sukͻ (koyi nhwene-pa) ma no, san yε nnyuma foforͻ wͻ εno akyi, na Yεn ara na na Yε’wεn wͻn"
  21,83,"Ayuub (Hiob) nso, εberε a ͻsu frεε ne Wura Nyankopͻn sε: “Nokorε ͻhaw ato me, na Wone Mmͻborͻhunufoͻ no mu Mmͻborͻhunu Hene no"
  21,84,"Enti Yε’gyee ne (sufrε no) so, yii ͻhaw a na ato no no frii neso, na Yε’de n’abusuafoͻ no ne nemmͻhoo bͻͻ hoo maa no εnam Yεn ahummͻborͻ nti; εyε afutusεm dema Nyame-somfoͻ no"
  21,85,Ne Ishmael ne Idriis ne Zul Kifil; wͻn nyinaa ka aboterεfoͻ no ho
  21,86,Yε’de wͻn (nyinaa) wuraa Y’ahummɔborɔ no mu. Nokorε sε wͻ’ka apapafoͻ no ho
  21,87,"Ɛne Zaa-Nuun (Yona), εberε a ͻde abufuo kͻeε no, na odwen sε Yε’mma ne ho nnkyere no, na osu frεε (Yεn) wͻ sum no mu sε: “Awuarade biara nni hͻ gyesε Wo. Kronkron Hene ne Wo! Nokorε, m’akͻka abͻneεfoͻ no ho”"
  21,88,"Enti Yε’gyee no so na Yε’gyee no fri ͻhaw ne awerεhoͻ no mu, na saa ara na Yε’gye agyidiefoͻ no (fri ͻhaw ne mmusuo mu)"
  21,89,"Ɛne Zakariya, εberε a osu frεε ne Wura Nyankopͻn sε: “Me Wura Nyankopͻn, enya me ankonam, na Wo na Woyε adedifoͻ no mu papa"
  21,90,"Enti Yε’gyee no so, maa no (ͻba a yεfrε no) Yahaya (Yohane), na Yε’saa ne yere yadeε (maa no woo ba) maa no. Nokorε sε na wͻ’si wͻn ho akan wͻ papayε ho, su frε Yεn wͻ anidaasoͻ ne suro mu; na wͻ’brε wͻn ho ase nso ma Yεn"
  21,91,"Ɛne (ͻbaa bunu Mar’yam) no a ͻhwεε ne ho so yie (wͻ nna mu) no, enti Yε’homee Yε’honhom guu ne mu, na Yε’de ͻne neba (Yesu) yεε nsεnkyerεnee maa amansan"
  21,92,"Nokorε sε, mo man woi yε ͻman baako, na Mene mo Wura Nyankopͻn, enti monsom Me"
  21,93,Nanso wͻ’paepaee wͻn ntεm wͻ wͻn dwumadie no ho. Yε’hͻ na obiara bεsan aba
  21,94,"Enti obia obedi dwuma pa na ͻyε gyidieni no, yεmpo ne mmͻdemmͻ a ͻbͻeε no, nokorε sε, Yε’twerε to hͻ ma no"
  21,95,"Nokorε, Ya’bra sε kuro (anaasε nnipa) a Y’asεe wͻn no, bεnsan aba (wiase) bio"
  21,96,Kͻpem sε yεbebue Yaajuuj ne Maajuuj (Gog ne Magog afri wͻn ban no mu) ama wabͻ yiridi apue afri simpie bea biara mu
  21,97,"Nokorε nso sɛ, bͻhyε (Da) no abεn. Na (sε nnipa sͻre fri adakamena mu a) wobehunu sε wͻn a wͻ’nnye nnie no ani ahaahae atͻ sa wͻ ehu mu. Wͻ’bεka sε: “Adi ayε yεn. Nokorε, na y’ani nna woi so, daabi na yε’yε abͻneεfoͻ”"
  21,98,"Nokorε sε, mo ne deε mofri Nyankopͻn akyi somoeε no, mone egya no nyentia, εmu na mobεtena afe bͻͻ"
  21,99,"Sε woi nom yε anyame ampa a, anka wͻ’mma (Amanehunu gya no mu) hͻ. Na emu na wͻn nyinaa bεtena afe bᴐᴐ"
  21,100,"Wͻ’bedi apenesie wͻ (egya no) mu, na emu no wͻ’nnte (kasa biara)"
  21,101,"Wͻn nso a papa adi kan afri Yεn hͻ akͻ wͻn hͻ no, wͻ’ne (Amanehunu gya no) ntεm kwan bεwa"
  21,102,"Wͻ’nnte (Ogya no) dede yε no ketewaa bi mpo, na deε εyε wͻn kraa akͻnnͻ no mu na wͻ’bεtena afe bͻͻ"
  21,103,"Wͻn werε nnho wͻ ehubͻ kεseε (Da) no ho, na Soro abͻfoͻ behyia wͻn (aka akyerε wͻn sε): “Woi ne moda no a yεhyεε mo ho bͻ no “"
  21,104,"(Kae) Ɛda no a Yε’bεbobͻ ͻsoro sεdeε yεbobͻ nwoma a εkyekyere kraataa ho no. Sεdeε Yε’hyεε kane abͻdeε no aseε no, saa ara na Yε’bεsan (de wͻn aba nkwa mu bio). (εyε) bͻhyε a εda Yεn soͻ. Nokorε nso sε Yε’bεyε"
  21,105,"Ampa sε Yε’twerεε no wͻ Dawid Nyom no mu wͻ afutusεm (a yεde maa Mose) no akyi sε: “Me nkoa apapafoͻ no na wͻ’bedi adeε wͻ asaase no soͻ"
  21,106,"Nokorε sε, amanebͻ (ahodoͻ) a εkͻ asomu wͻ (saa Qur’aan) yi mu de ma nnipa a wͻ’som (Nyame)"
  21,107,"(Nkͻmhyεni), deε enti Yε’somaaa woͻ ne sε, (wogyina hͻ sε) ahummͻborͻ dema amansan nyinaa"
  21,108,"(Nkͻmhyεni), kasε: “Medeε yayi akyerε me sε: “Mo Nyankopͻn no yε Nyankopͻn baako, na enti mobεbrε mo ho ase ayε Muslimifoͻ anaa?”"
  21,109,"Sε wͻ’dane wͻn ho (fri nokorε no ho) a, εneε ka sε: “(Asεm no ho) kͻkͻ pεpεεpε na mede abͻ mo nyinaa no, na mennim sε ebia deε yahyε mo ho bͻ no abεn anaasε εwͻ akyiri"
  21,110,"Nokorε sε, Onim asεm a moka ma no pue εna Onim deε mode suma"
  21,111,"Mennim sε ebia (twεn a Nyankopͻn retwentwεn asotwee no soͻ no) yε nsͻhwε ma mo, anaasε (Ͻde mamo) agye moani akͻpem εberε bi"
  21,112,"(Nkͻmhyεni) ka sε: “Me Wura Nyankopͻn, fa Nokorε no bu atεn. Ye’Wura Nyankopͻn, Ahummͻborͻ Hene no, Nemmoa na yεhwehwε tia deε mode susu (no) no"